  30 May 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> lockdev-1.0.3.1.2-r3.ebuild:
  Fix Perl module build to use relative ${PERL_S}.

*lockdev-1.0.3.1.2-r3 (21 May 2014)

